title: Sketchbook Folio, "Rough Sea and Dark Cliffs under Stormy Sky", 1870–85
medium: Graphite on cream wove paper, bound
provenance: Anna Richards Brewster, Scarsdale, NY, 1905-1952; William T. Brewster
creditline: Gift of the National Academy of Design from the Mrs. William T. Brewster Bequest
description: Dark, choppy water across foreground. At left, in middleground, rocks and then large cliffs in three sections. Dark, stormy sky overhead.
